_alpha201.shtml |accessdate=June 7, 2009 |quote=Alpha continues to stand as the organization that represents the totality of the Black male...}}</ref>}} {{mem/f |name=Joshua Smith |chapter=[[Central State University|Delta Xi]] |nota=CEO of Maxima Corporation |ref=<ref name=soa/>}} }}
